The most effective opposition to **The Terra Continuum** would not come from a single entity, but from a **coalition of incumbents** who control the three pillars of global power: **Military Force**, **Capital**, and **Public Narrative**.

I will call this coalition **The Realist Bloc**.

They are not villains in their own eyes; they are defenders of **Sovereignty, Prosperity, and Liberty** as currently defined. They possess the leverage to kill the framework before it is born because they control the infrastructure required to enforce it.

